    "body": "Concept ACK\r\n\r\nI think you may also need to adjust `_POSIX_C_SOURCE` in your autoconf test - see:\r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/694f4cbd7853ffeb7b4576d42368920b0ef79b01/src/util/system.cpp#L20-L29\r\n\r\nContext:\r\nhttps://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Feature-Test-Macros.html#index-_005fPOSIX_005fC_005fSOURCE\r\nhttp://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man3/posix_fallocate.3.html#CONFORMING_TO\r\n\r\nPerhaps we could check the defined version rather than adjusting it ourselves?",
